{"1":{"w":[{"b":"0.15","h":"0.7","c":"إِنَّا","d":"innā","e":"innā"},{"b":"2.9","h":"2.13","c":"أَنْزَلْنَاهُ","d":"anzalnāhu","e":"anzalnāhu"},{"b":"5.4","h":"6.6","c":"فِي","d":"fī","e":"fī"},{"b":"5.8","h":"7.5","c":"لَيْلَةِ","d":"laylati","e":"laylati"},{"b":"6.7","h":"8.99","c":"الْقَدْرِ","d":"l-qadri","e":"l-qadri"}],"a":{"g":"Indeed, We sent the Qur'an down during the Night of Decree.","ihya":"\n        <div class=\"ihya-tafsir-box\" style=\"margin-top: 15px; border-top: 1px solid #eee; padding-top: 10px;\">\n            <h5 style=\"color: #91740c; font-family: Cabin, sans-serif;\">Tafsir Al-Ihya</h5>\n            <div class=\"ihya-arabic\" style=\"font-family: IndoPak; font-size: 18px; text-align: right; margin-bottom: 10px; color: #555;\">\n                ومنها الإيجار بالحذف والإضمار كقوله تعالى ﴿ إنا أنزلناه في ليلة القدر ﴾ {} أراد القرآن وما سبق له ذكر\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"ihya-english\" style=\"font-family: Arial; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify; color: #777;\">\n                Indeed, We sent it down on the Night of Decree [Laylat al-Qadr] — meaning the Qur'an [al-Qur'an], for which mention has preceded.\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        "}},"2":{"w":[{"b":"0.04","h":"0.45","c":"وَمَا","d":"wamā","e":"wamā"},{"b":"0.4","h":"2.48","c":"أَدْرَاكَ","d":"adrāka","e":"adrāka"},{"b":"3.2","h":"4.27","c":"مَا","d":"mā","e":"mā"},{"b":"3.6","h":"5.05","c":"لَيْلَةُ","d":"laylatu","e":"laylatu"},{"b":"4.4","h":"6.51","c":"الْقَدْرِ","d":"l-qadri","e":"l-qadri"}],"a":{"g":"And what can make you know what is the Night of Decree?"}},"3":{"w":[{"b":"0.15","h":"0.35","c":"لَيْلَةُ","d":"laylatu","e":"laylatu"},{"b":"0.88","h":"1.6","c":"الْقَدْرِ","d":"l-qadri","e":"l-qadri"},{"b":"1.6","h":"2.89","c":"خَيْرٌ","d":"khayrun","e":"khayrun"},{"b":"3.3","h":"4.95","c":"مِنْ","d":"min","e":"min"},{"b":"3.6","h":"5.57","c":"أَلْفِ","d":"alfi","e":"alfi"},{"b":"4.2","h":"6.72","c":"شَهْرٍ","d":"shahrin","e":"shahrin"}],"a":{"g":